Normally I copy my 'server' edition wikis into `./public/wikis`. However, if you already have a directory containing your 'server' edition wikis then can change 'appdir' to point to that directory.

> The 'server' edition wikis are NOT updated by tw5-mws-loader. Wikis in that directory are read and loaded into the MWS Database as recipes. Changes done on MWS database to those wikis/recipes do not update the 'server' edition wikis.

